IONNIC BBS-TEK MEDIUM DUTY SQUAWKER

Ionnic BBS-TEK Medium Duty Squawker available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Features;

  • Unique multi-frequency white sound.
  • Eliminates noise nuisance complaints.
  • Sound confined to the danger zone.
  • Instantly locatable sound.
  • Environmentally sealed – IP68.
  • Epoxy filled for maximum vibration resistance.
  • Can be steam & pressure cleaned.
  • Multi-voltage.
  • Lifetime warranty.

Specifications;

  • Output: 77, 82, 87, 92, 97 dB(A) @ 1m
  • Voltage: 12-24V
  • Body: AES
  • Cable Length: 1m
  • Vibration: 10G
  • EMC: CE & ‘e’ marked
  • Standards: SAE J994 environmental
  • Operating Temp: -40°C to 85°C
  • IP Rating: IP68

To view the full range of products available for your 4×4, CLICK HERE!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
